\u064e\u0627\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0629\u064d","numberInSurah":7,"juz":30},{"number":6165,"text":"\u0648\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062e\u064e\u0641\u0651\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0632\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064f\u0647\u064f","numberInSurah":8,"juz":30},{"number":6166,"text":"\u0641\u064e\u0623\u064f\u0645\u0651\u064f\u0647\u064f \u0647\u064e\u0627\u0648\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0629\u064c","numberInSurah":9,"juz":30},{"number":6167,"text":"\u0648\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u062f\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0643\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0647\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0647\u0652","numberInSurah":10,"juz":30},{"number":6168,"text":"\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064c \u062d\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0629\u064c","numberInSurah":11,"juz":30}],"edition":{"identifier":"quran-simple","language":"ar","name":"Simple","englishName":"Simple","format":"text","type":"quran"}},{"number":101,"name":"\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0642\u0627\u0631\u0639\u0629","englishName":"Al-Qaari'a","englishNameTranslation":"The Calamity","revelationType":"Meccan","numberOfAyahs":11,"ayahs":[{"text":"In the name of God, The Most Gracious, The Dispenser of Grace:"},{"number":6158,"text":"OH, the sudden calamity!","numberInSurah":1,"juz":30},{"number":6159,"text":"How awesome the sudden calamity!","numberInSurah":2,"juz":30},{"number":6160,"text":"And what could make thee conceive what that sudden calamity will be?","numberInSurah":3,"juz":30},{"number":6161,"text":"[It will occur] on the Day when men will be like moths swarming in confusion,","numberInSurah":4,"juz":30},{"number":6162,"text":"and the mountains will be like fluffy tufts of wool....","numberInSurah":5,"juz":30},{"number":6163,"text":"And then, he whose weight [of good deeds] is heavy in the balance","numberInSurah":6,"juz":30},{"number":6164,"text":"shall find himself in a happy' state of life;","numberInSurah":7,"juz":30},{"number":6165,"text":"whereas he whose weight is light in the balance","numberInSurah":8,"juz":30},{"number":6166,"text":"shall be engulfed by an abyss.","numberInSurah":9,"juz":30},{"number":6167,"text":"And what could make thee conceive what that [abyss] will be?","numberInSurah":10,"juz":30},{"number":6168,"text":"A fire hotly burning!","numberInSurah":11,"juz":30}],"edition":{"identifier":"en.asad","language":"en","name":"Asad","englishName":"Muhammad Asad","format":"text","type":"translation"}}]}